    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一支舰队已整装待发，而您，即将踏入这片群雄割据、机遇与挑战并存的广袤星河。在这里，您将与星际海盗殊死搏斗，亲历各大势力间的恩怨情仇，开展贸易，扩充舰队，探索遗落在宇宙深处的秘密与财宝。随着财富与军事力量的不断积累，您也将逐步拥有左右宇宙格局的力量……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >踏上星河之旅</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等待您的是一片名为星河的浩瀚舞台。您可以在璀璨星海中自由书写属于自己的传奇，组建舰队、发展贸易、割据一方。在通往星海霸主的路上，潜藏着足以令整个宇宙动荡不安的终局危机……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187610/extras/4ca8e7d59fcc4f718116be6755541409.poster.avif?t=1750519434\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187610/extras/4ca8e7d59fcc4f718116be6755541409.webm?t=1750519434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187610/extras/4ca8e7d59fcc4f718116be6755541409.mp4?t=1750519434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拟真的经济系统 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内置了基于供需关系动态变化的经济系统。每一场战争，每一笔交易，都会悄然改变星河经济的天平。这片星空中蕴藏着无数商机，善于洞察时局的商人，总能在混乱与秩序之间寻找致富之道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187610/extras/f298144cf7d224dbb73349a579d9321a.poster.avif?t=1750519434\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187610/extras/f298144cf7d224dbb73349a579d9321a.webm?t=1750519434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187610/extras/f298144cf7d224dbb73349a579d9321a.mp4?t=1750519434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >爽快的弹幕战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宇宙中跨越无数天文单位的辽阔战场，将每一场战斗变成华丽的弹幕盛宴。弹幕如繁星绽放，战斗仿佛在无尽深空中上演的芭蕾舞剧。带上最顶尖的装备与最娴熟的技巧，在一场场壮丽的星际交响中闪耀登场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187610/extras/9045112a72c263a6840508eb2f269572.poster.avif?t=1750519434\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187610/extras/9045112a72c263a6840508eb2f269572.webm?t=1750519434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187610/extras/9045112a72c263a6840508eb2f269572.mp4?t=1750519434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >书写你的太空史诗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从指挥舰队参与星际冲突，到统领势力扩张版图，再到引领整个银河抵御终局危机，您将在不同的层面施展战略与战术才华。通过多样化的事件探索宇宙深处的故事，每一个决定，都可能让星河走向截然不同的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187610/extras/36f7f3c1d03f00ebd9b1a1e13064eb8b.poster.avif?t=1750519434\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187610/extras/36f7f3c1d03f00ebd9b1a1e13064eb8b.webm?t=1750519434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187610/extras/36f7f3c1d03f00ebd9b1a1e13064eb8b.mp4?t=1750519434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
